step.para:
		tdbdump
		/etc/samba/secrets.tdb
		If the tdbdump is installed on your system (not essential),
		you can look inside the /etc/samba/secrets.tdb file. If
		you wish to do this, execute:

&rootprompt; tdbdump secrets.tdb
